@JohnWM
I used to live in a basement apartment a few years back, and I would often have to raise my phone high up above my head to get a signal. I was right next to the parking lot, so the view out my window was always a truck tire. Whenever someone walked past outside, it would interrupt my TV antenna's signal.

Happily, I no longer live in a hole.

